 1735                                                       ;The following subroutine, used by various sections of
 1736                                                       ;SCELBAL, will search the LINE INPUT BUGGER for
 1737                                                       ;a character string which is contained in a buffer starting
 1738                                                       ;at the address pointed to by CPU registers H & L when
 1739                                                       ;the subroutine is entered.
